1_28

functions:
	pure function: just return values
		eg: abs, pow, ...
	non-pure functions: have side effects, could also return values
		eg: print, play_sound, ...

def statement
	name, formal parameter, body(+ return statement)

call expression: square(2+2)
	operator: square, operand 2+2, argument: 4
	*** when you call a function, a new frame is created

environment and names
	name are evaluated to the value bound to that name in the earliest frame of the current environment

statement, clause, header, suit
	statement: the whole thing
	???

